author: rhuijben
msg: Simplify a lot of if conditions in the update editors merge_file() function
based on the simple assumption that this function is not called for shadowed
and obstructed nodes.
This patch is the logic change. A followup patch will change the whitespace
and layout.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/update_editor.c
(merge_file): Assume that we are not called for shadowed files. Check for
obstructions once instead of on every condition. Remove some dead code
which checked if a local file was identical to its new base.
Only retrieve pristine abspath when we really need it. Assume that the
local file is always there (or it would have been reinstalled in an
earlier phase of the update).
(close_file): Assume a constant result for obstructed files.
